column2: Cheer 15 bits or more with a HEX code attatched to change the color of my lights! If you cheer 100 bits or sub, special effects will happen as well!
Want to join my discord for announcements on when I go live, polls, or other things in general? Click this link to join: https://discord.gg/X9zW8e3 !
My plan for learning this game can be found here: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1s02_YkAZigbetKKvWOZn1G136GgRRQyWdkGWEajO7ls/edit?usp=sharing
